Step 1:install telegram and login with you phone number 
Step 2:Go to search and type " BotFather " 
Step 3:click ok  on " BotFather" 
Step 4: type  " /start " and send 
Step 5:something come from BotFather and go to " /newbot " and click ok
Step 6: something come from BotFather like this " Alright,
 a new bot. How are we going to call it?" 
 Please choose a name for your bot. "
Step 7: example: sagar123Bot or Sagar786_bot. Type and send
Step 8: when your name valid BotFather send you message successful congratulation
Step 9: BotFather send your " API " and use this API in your Practical. 
